name: end time - memento mori
description:
This animated flyer is a giveaway to celebrate the final Halloween party (in a long series) thrown at the Snake Pit, a well loved location in Dane County, WI, USA. 

The party will run from 9 PM on October 30th until dawn of Halloween morning.

These were amazing parties and I was very happy to help with some last minute artwork to commemorate the night. I hope that if you are watching this from somewhere else in the world that at least this is an interesting example of CLIP guided diffusion..
